            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="32160621">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">Say not, &quot; I have found the truth,&quot; but rather, &quot; I have found a truth.&quot;
Say not, &quot; I have found the path of the soul.&quot; Say rather, &quot; I have met the soul walking upon my path.&quot;

